    "The model incorporates a description of the hardware and software environment, its hyperparameters, a strategy for dividing the dataset into training and testing sets, and various metrics for comparing different models.",
    "All these factors are important for providing reliable, reproducible results.",
    "Table 4 below summarises all configurations used within our experiments: hyperparameters, environment hardware and software, train-test splits, and evaluation criteria.",
    "The experimental setup was done in such a way that the robust performance of the proposed PolynetDWTCADx framework in colorectal cancer detection and segmentation was ensured.",
    "The proposed system utilized CNNs for feature extraction, such as ResNet-50, DenseNet-201, and VGG-16, by initializing these models with ImageNet weights since these models were optimized for feature extraction."
